To PEKA:
You can get the minerals from the plant surface of a level only when you land successfully for the first time. After landing, you can go out from your envelope. Walking to those large green crystals to get the minerals, they will be counted as soon as you return to your envelope. If you have failed in landing that level before, you will not find any crystals on the surface. It will only regenerate after many days. If you want to land on some plants other than Soupaline, you have to get your space suit

On demand in the French forum, I've created a little script that can be used for more interaction between AlphaBounce and the MineMap.
